Project Title

Road Damage Detection System Using Image Processing and Machine Learning
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Problem Statement

Road damages such as potholes, cracks, and surface defects are common causes of accidents, vehicle damage, and traffic problems. Manual road inspection is time-consuming, costly, and may not detect damages quickly. Therefore, there is a need for an automated system that can accurately identify road damages from images and help authorities take timely maintenance actions.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project Objectives
To detect road damages such as potholes and cracks automatically.
To reduce the time and effort required for manual road inspection.
To improve road safety by identifying damaged roads at an early stage.
To provide accurate and reliable damage detection results.
To assist government authorities in road maintenance planning.
To develop a user-friendly system for reporting and monitoring road conditions.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Module List
Module 1: User Interface Module
Provides a simple interface for users.
Allows users to upload road images.
Displays the detection results.
Module 2: Image Acquisition Module
Collects road images from cameras or uploaded files.
Stores images for processing.
Module 3: Image Preprocessing Module
Improves image quality.
Removes noise and unwanted distortions.
Resizes images for analysis.
Module 4: Road Damage Detection Module
Detects potholes, cracks, and other road defects.
Uses image processing and machine learning techniques.
Classifies the type of damage.
Module 5: Result Analysis Module
Displays detected damages with labels.
Calculates detection accuracy.
Generates analysis reports.
Module 6: Database Management Module
Stores uploaded images and detection results.
Maintains records for future reference.
Module 7: Reporting and Notification Module
Generates road damage reports.
Helps authorities identify damaged locations.
Supports timely maintenance decisions.
